                         "originalText":  "Local Intel, AI, Scenario Copilot",
                         "lineHeight":  1.25,
                         "baseline":  28
                     },
                     {
                         "id":  "t_ai_body",
                         "type":  "text",
                         "x":  862,
                         "y":  1548,
                         "width":  665,
                         "height":  342,
                         "angle":  0,
                         "strokeColor":  "#1e1e1e",
                         "backgroundColor":  "transparent",
                         "fillStyle":  "solid",
                         "strokeWidth":  1,
                         "strokeStyle":  "solid",
                         "roughness":  1,
                         "opacity":  100,
                         "groupIds":  [

                                      ],
                         "frameId":  null,
                         "roundness":  null,
                         "seed":  503,
                         "version":  1,
                         "versionNonce":  503,
                         "isDeleted":  false,
                         "boundElements":  null,
                         "updated":  1,
                         "link":  null,
                         "locked":  false,
                         "text":  "Local intel:\n- Calendar events and manager-entered events are scored deterministically.\n- Outputs demand shock, ADR headroom, confidence, evidence, and guardrails.\n- Context does not change ADR unless the manager approves it.\n\nAI / copilot:\n- Pricing agent runs data ingestion, optimizer, pace analyst, strategist, validation.\n- DeepSeek writes manager-facing explanations, not autonomous prices.\n- Scenario Copilot answers date, ranking, market, local intel, and audit questions.\n- Scenario drafts require confirmation before simulation.\n- Grounding checks block unsupported numbers, prompt injection, and skipped approval.\n\nKey files:\n- src/pricing_core/local_intel.py\n- src/copilot_core/scenario_copilot.py\n- src/copilot_core/scenario_llm_copilot.py",
                         "fontSize":  17,
                         "fontFamily":  1,
                         "textAlign":  "left",
                         "verticalAlign":  "top",
                         "containerId":  null,
                         "originalText":  "Local intel:\n- Calendar events and manager-entered events are scored deterministically.\n- Outputs demand shock, ADR headroom, confidence, evidence, and guardrails.\n- Context does not change ADR unless the manager approves it.\n\nAI / copilot:\n- Pricing agent runs data ingestion, optimizer, pace analyst, strategist, validation.\n- DeepSeek writes manager-facing explanations, not autonomous prices.\n- Scenario Copilot answers date, ranking, market, local intel, and audit questions.\n- Scenario drafts require confirmation before simulation.\n- Grounding checks block unsupported numbers, prompt injection, and skipped approval.\n\nKey files:\n- src/pricing_core/local_intel.py\n- src/copilot_core/scenario_copilot.py\n- src/copilot_core/scenario_llm_copilot.py",
                         "lineHeight":  1.25,
                         "baseline":  300
